+ Parameters
    + locatedWithin: `{"type":"Polygon","coordinates":[[12,53],[14,53],[13,52.9]]}` (string, required) - polygon, [longitude,latitude]
    + validFrom: `2017-07-01T00:00:00Z` (string, required) - ISO8601 timestamp notation, means incl. this timestamp; always provide a time offset, e.g. 'Z' for UTC; optional: a request may provide correct offset (so that server can convert to UTC).
    + validUntil: `2017-07-01T01:00:00Z` (string, required) - ISO8601 timestamp notation, means incl. this timestamp; always provide a time offset, e.g. 'Z' for UTC; optional: a request may provide correct offset (so that server can convert to UTC).
    + validPeriod: `PT0S` (string, required) - comma separated list of periods to be retrieved.
    + fields: `maxThunderstormProbabilityInPercent` (string, required) - comma separated list of parameters to be contained inside response.

